  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>The Song of the Rhoyne</b></i> is a play.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Song_of_the_Rhoyne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Song_of_the_Rhoyne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Mummer\" title=\"Mummer\">mummers</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/The_Ship\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Ship\">the Ship</a> teach <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a> the speeches from <i>The Song of the <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoyne\" title=\"Rhoyne\">Rhoyne</a></i>, <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Conqueror%27s_Two_Wives\" title=\"The Conqueror&#39;s Two Wives\">The Conqueror's Two Wives</a></i> and <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Merchant%27s_Lusty_Lady\" title=\"The Merchant&#39;s Lusty Lady\">The Merchant's Lusty Lady</a></i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Song_of_the_Rhoyne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhove